I’m not affiliated with 4788, but am intrigued by their 2025 robot. I haven’t found a public cad file yet, their website has a spot for one but nothing is linked to it; if clicked you get redirected to the home page. If someone has knowledge if its publicly available it would be greatly appreciated.

Hi @Nathan1, this has prompted us to finish our post , which you can now find here:

4788 Can't Control - CAD, Code, and Technical + Outreach Documentation Release General Forum
We’re pleased to release our CAD, Code, and Technical + Outreach Documentation for 2025 Reefscape. At least one person asked for it , and we meant to do it earlier. CAD CODE Robot Reveal + Our Favourite Match Technical Binder Outreach Binder Impact Essay + Exec Summary We are happy to answer all questions, as soon as is possible for us! We have our final event this coming weekend, which you can watch here [image]

It’s funny you found our website, it is still under construction… !
